      <h3>The Board of Directors 2025-26</h3>
      <p>We are fortunate to have a talented International Board of Directors. There are 17 Directors from 10 different countries. We meet once a month online.</p>

      <img src="/images/2026/05/board.png" alt="The Board of Directors of the International Rotary Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals">

      <p>The International Rotary Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals (IRFHP) is led by an international Board of Directors who meet monthly online. Directors are elected in accordance with the Fellowship&rsquo;s Constitution and Bylaws, ensuring transparent and accountable governance.</p>
      <p>As one of Rotary&rsquo;s most active Fellowships, we maintain a vibrant programme of global activities, professional exchanges, humanitarian initiatives, and collaborative learning. We warmly encourage members to connect with us, participate in our work, and strengthen our shared impact.</p>
      <p>If you wish to contact any member of the Board, we would be pleased to hear from you.</p>
      <p>CONTACT: <a href="mailto:rotaryhealthprofessionals@gmail.com">rotaryhealthprofessionals@gmail.com</a></p>

